title: MTS Football/Baseball Crossover Part 2: Manager, Former Players and Media Members
itunes:title: MTS Football/Baseball Crossover Part 2: Manager, Former Players and Media Members
description:
Move the Sticks presents a special crossover episode focusing on Football and Baseball team building, how they relate and differ. Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks got to talk to a wide array of influential voices in the MLB. Part two will focus on former players, managers and media members talking about how the teams compare.
